metadata.name: "Team Tailgate" from Tailgate Tavern
metadata.description:
Team Tailgate' is an exciting new Membership Program that offers Members a wide range of perks and benefits that are only available to Team Tailgate Members. We are limiting this exclusive offer to be part of the club to only 100 Memberships and once they are all sold you can only purchase one from a current member that wants to sell it, so buy yours now and own it for life!

[Learn More](https://app.getstakes.io/public/token/10)
